Package: libsodium-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libsodium4 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Portable, packageable NaCl-based crypto library (development files)
 libsodium is a software library for network communication,
 encryption,decryption, signatures, etc.
 .
 libsodium is a portable, cross-compilable, installable, packageable,
 API-compatible version of NaCl.
 .
 This package contains development files for libsodium.

